# Language Policy

IMPORTANT: Follow these language settings strictly for all work in this project.

- **Code comments**: Write all code comments, docstrings, and inline documentation in {{.Language.Comments}}
- **Commit messages**: Write all git commit messages in {{.Language.Commits}}
